# Portfolio new project ‚Äî fill modal prompt

When the user adds a new portfolio project, produce **every field** below in a copy-paste block for **Admin ‚Üí Portfolio ‚Üí Add project**. Match tone and length of existing entries in `assets/js/portfolio-built-in-data.js` (Pro Cleaning, Grippy Socks, Lawn Care).

## Ask the user for (if not provided)

- Project / client name
- Live demo URL (or `#` if none)
- Screenshot filename (must live in `assets/images/` as `project-{slug}.png`)
- App type: mobile (Expo/RN), web, or both
- Optional: buy-now pricing, premium tier, target customers

## Output format (use exactly these labels)

```markdown
## Portfolio project ‚Äî {Title}

**Title:**  
**Filter category:** `professional` | `creative`  
**Live project URL:**  
**Project screenshot:** `/assets/images/project-{slug}.png`  
**Image alt text:**  
**Description:** (2‚Äì4 sentences; card + detail modal)  
**Tech stack:** (comma-separated)  
**Outcome:** (optional; 1‚Äì2 sentences, shown as ‚ÄúOutcome:‚Äù in modal)  
**Buy now label:** (optional, e.g. `Buy Now: $500`)  
**Premium label:** (optional, e.g. `Premium with Customizations: $750 - $1,000`)  
**Show quote button:** yes | no  
**Detail modal ‚Äî admin focus:** (optional; operations/admin dashboard angle)  
**Best for:** (optional; one audience per line)

---

### Checklist before save
- [ ] Screenshot saved as `assets/images/project-{slug}.png` (16:9 or similar; ~1200px+ wide)
- [ ] `firebase deploy --only hosting` after adding **new** image files
- [ ] Image URL uses `/assets/images/...` (leading slash) or pick from dropdown after deploy
- [ ] Preview in modal shows the screenshot (not coming-soon placeholder)
- [ ] Category matches Portfolio filter (Professional vs Creative)
```

## Field rules

| Field | Rules |
|--------|--------|
| **Title** | Client or product name; max 200 chars |
| **Category** | `professional` = client apps / production work; `creative` = demos, experiments, template sites |
| **Live URL** | Full `https://...` or `#` if private / not deployed |
| **Image** | Path `/assets/images/project-{kebab-slug}.png` only for repo assets; external URLs allowed for hosted images |
| **Image alt** | Short screen-reader label, e.g. `{Name} app homepage` |
| **Description** | What it does, who it‚Äôs for, key features; no bullet lists unless user asks |
| **Tech stack** | Real stack only: `React Native`, `Expo`, `Firebase`, `Node`, etc. |
| **Outcome** | Measurable or concrete result; omit if none |
| **Buy labels** | Only for template / white-label products you sell |
| **Show quote** | Default **yes** unless user says otherwise |
| **Admin note** | What the `/admin` (or owner) dashboard handles‚Äîbookings, orders, messages, etc. |
| **Best for** | 3‚Äì5 short audience lines for detail modal chips |

